\c 148 Zvose zvakasikwa ngazvirumbidze Jehovha 1 Hareruya! Rumbidzai Jehovha, imi muri kudenga; Murumbidzei panzvimbo dzokumusoro. 2 Murumbidzei imi vatumwa vake vose; Murumbidzei imi hondo dzake dzose. 3 Murumbidzei imi zuva Murumbidzei imi nyeredzi dzose dzinovhenekera. 4 Murumbidzei imi kudenga kwokudenga-denga, Newe mvura zhinji, iri kumusoro
